<arggraph id="micro_c045" topic_id="influence_of_recycling" stance="pro">
  <edu id="e1"><![CDATA[Recycling really does make a difference]]></edu>
  <edu id="e2"><![CDATA[because without it, there would be an abundance of paper, glass, and plastic.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e3"><![CDATA[If we did not recycle, before long there would be nowhere to put all of the extra garbage.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e4"><![CDATA[Recycling helps the environment]]></edu>
  <edu id="e5"><![CDATA[by keeping non-natural things out of it.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e6"><![CDATA[This way, animals do not accidentally eat it and get sick or die.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e7"><![CDATA[It also helps keep plastics, which are not biodegradable, out of the environment, and from getting into our water supplies.]]></edu>
